# JavaScript — A Learning Journey
### by Minahil

---

A structured, documented path through JavaScript — from fundamentals to advanced concepts. Each concept has its own folder, notes, and practice code.

---

## Structure

​```
JavaScript-Journey/
│
├── Phase-1-Fundamentals/
│   ├── 01-Variables/
│   ├── 02-Data-Types/
│   ├── 03-Operators/
│   ├── 04-Conditionals/
│   ├── 05-Loops/
│   └── 06-Functions/
│
├── Phase-2-Intermediate/
│   ├── 01-Arrays/
│   ├── 02-Objects/
│   ├── 03-DOM-Manipulation/
│   ├── 04-Events/
│   └── 05-ES6+/
│
├── Phase-3-Async/
│   ├── 01-Callbacks/
│   ├── 02-Promises/
│   └── 03-Async-Await/
│
└── Phase-4-Advanced/
    ├── 01-Closures/
    ├── 02-Prototypes/
    ├── 03-Design-Patterns/
    └── 04-Projects/
​```

Each folder contains a `.js` file with practice code and a `README.md` with notes on that concept.

